text: Coedydd a Cheunant Rheidol (Rheidol Woods & Gorge) is a Site of Special Scientific Interest in Ceredigion, west Wales. ==See also== *List of Sites of Special Scientific Interest in Ceredigion Category:Sites of Special Scientific Interest in Ceredigion
